    base:desc "
    **Industry Standards & Compliance:**
    - **Open-Source Adoption:**
      - Hardware/software specifications available via GitHub ([link](https://github.com/INTO-CPS-Association/example-incubator)).
      - RabbitMQ (open-source message broker; no explicit compliance to industry standards).
    - **Technical Standards:**
